(10465, '_transient_8e427eb76a187f7942598aa1bd630850', '\n<div class="ngg-albumoverview">	\n	<!-- List of galleries -->\n	\n	<div class="ngg-album">\n		<div class="ngg-albumtitle"><a href="http://www.joecora.com/?page_id=81">Wedding</a></div>\n			<div class="ngg-albumcontent">\n				<div class="ngg-thumbnail">\n					<a href="http://www.joecora.com/?page_id=81"><img class="Thumb" alt="Wedding" src="http://www.joecora.com/wp-content/gallery/wedding/dynamic/img_9115-1-nggid0246-ngg0dyn-160x120x100-00f0w010c011r110f110r010t010.jpg"/></a>\n				</div>\n				<div class="ngg-description">\n				<p>你微微地笑着，不同我说什么话，而我觉得，为了这个，我已等待得很久了。</p>\n							</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n\n 	\n	<div class="ngg-album">\n		<div class="ngg-albumtitle"><a href="http://www.joecora.com/?page_id=98">Park</a></div>\n			<div class="ngg-albumcontent">\n				<div class="ngg-thumbnail">\n					<a href="http://www.joecora.com/?page_id=98"><img class="Thumb" alt="Park" src="http://www.joecora.com/wp-content/gallery/park/dynamic/img_9116-1-nggid0251-ngg0dyn-160x120x100-00f0w010c011r110f110r010t010.jpg"/></a>\n				</div>\n				<div class="ngg-description">\n				<p>一片绿地，一抺阳光，一线闪光，便是你和我，最美的一幕</p>\n							</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n\n 	\n	<div class="ngg-album">\n		<div class="ngg-albumtitle"><a href="http://www.joecora.com/?page_id=163">Beach</a></div>\n			<div class="ngg-albumcontent">\n				<div class="ngg-thumbnail">\n					<a href="http://www.joecora.com/?page_id=163"><img class="Thumb" alt="Beach" src="http://www.joecora.com/wp-content/gallery/beach/dynamic/img_9162-1-nggid0266-ngg0dyn-160x120x100-00f0w010c011r110f110r010t010.jpg"/></a>\n				</div>\n				<div class="ngg-description">\n				<p>我们说的地平线，古人叫它天涯</p>\n							</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n\n 	\n	<div class="ngg-album">\n		<div class="ngg-albumtitle"><a href="http://www.joecora.com/?page_id=162">Play</a></div>\n			<div class="ngg-albumcontent">\n				<div class="ngg-thumbnail">\n					<a href="http://www.joecora.com/?page_id=162"><img class="Thumb" alt="Play" src="http://www.joecora.com/wp-content/gallery/play/dynamic/img_9283-1-nggid0269-ngg0dyn-160x120x100-00f0w010c011r110f110r010t010.jpg"/></a>\n				</div>\n				<div class="ngg-description">\n				<p>生命就应该浪费在美丽的事情上面</p>\n							</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n\n 	\n	<div class="ngg-album">\n		<div class="ngg-albumtitle"><a href="http://www.joecora.com/?page_id=164">Traditional</a></div>\n			<div class="ngg-albumcontent">\n				<div class="ngg-thumbnail">\n					<a href="http://www.joecora.com/?page_id=164"><img class="Thumb" alt="Traditional" src="http://www.joecora.com/wp-content/gallery/traditional/dynamic/img_9367-1-nggid0277-ngg0dyn-160x120x100-00f0w010c011r110f110r010t010.jpg"/></a>\n				</div>\n				<div class="ngg-description">\n				<p>如果我的生命中没有智慧，它仅仅会黯然失色；如果我的生命中没有爱情，它就会毁灭</p>\n							</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n\n 	 	\n	<!-- Pagination -->\n 	<div class=''ngg-clear''></div> 	\n</div>\n\n', 'no'),
