(327, 1, '2014-04-18 10:15:53', '2014-04-18 02:15:53', '给git上代理很简单,命令一下就可以了,如下:\r\n\r\n\r\n<blockquote>$ git config --global http.proxy 127.0.0.1:8087\r\n$ git config --global https.proxy 127.0.0.1:8087</blockquote>\r\n\r\n除此之外还需要配置goagent证书：设置SSL证书的位置\r\n\r\n<blockquote>$ git config --global http.sslCAinfo /d/GoAgent/CA.crt</blockquote>\r\n\r\n取消代理也很简单,如下:\r\n\r\n<blockquote>$ git config --global http.proxy ""\r\n$ git config --global https.proxy ""\r\n$ git config --global http.sslCAinfo ""</blockquote>\r\n\r\n\r\n', '给Git设置goagent代理或取消代理', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e7%bb%99git%e8%ae%be%e7%bd%aegoagent%e4%bb%a3%e7%90%86%e6%88%96%e5%8f%96%e6%b6%88%e4%bb%a3%e7%90%86', '', '', '2014-04-18 10:15:53', '2014-04-18 02:15:53', '', 0, 'http://www.joecora.com/?p=327', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(328, 1, '2014-04-18 10:15:53', '2014-04-18 02:15:53', '给git上代理很简单,命令一下就可以了,如下:\r\n\r\n\r\n<blockquote>$ git config --global http.proxy 127.0.0.1:8087\r\n$ git config --global https.proxy 127.0.0.1:8087</blockquote>\r\n\r\n除此之外还需要配置goagent证书：设置SSL证书的位置\r\n\r\n<blockquote>$ git config --global http.sslCAinfo /d/GoAgent/CA.crt</blockquote>\r\n\r\n取消代理也很简单,如下:\r\n\r\n<blockquote>$ git config --global http.proxy ""\r\n$ git config --global https.proxy ""\r\n$ git config --global http.sslCAinfo ""</blockquote>\r\n\r\n\r\n', '给Git设置goagent代理或取消代理', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '327-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-18 10:15:53', '2014-04-18 02:15:53', '', 327, 'http://www.joecora.com/?p=328', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
