(541, 1, '2014-05-16 11:32:09', '2014-05-16 03:32:09', '在win7下安装的步骤是：\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<pre><code>C:\\&gt; npm install -g phonegap</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<pre><code>$ phonegap create my-app\r\n$ cd my-app\r\n$ phonegap run android</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n但中间遇到许多问题，在这个环境下是遇到的问题及解决方式如下：\r\n\r\n<strong>1 . 大意是 ant 无法执行：</strong>\r\n\r\n解决方法是：下载最新版ant:  http://apache.fayea.com/apache-mirror//ant/binaries/apache-ant-1.9.4-bin.zip.\r\n<h1>Installing Ant on Windows</h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Enter the URL: <a href="http://ant.apache.org/bindownload.cgi" target="_blank">http://ant.apache.org/bindownload.cgi</a> .</li>\r\n	<li>On the Apache Ant Project page, find the heading Current Release of Ant .</li>\r\n	<li>Select apache-ant-1.6.5-bin.zip [PGP] [SHA1] [MD5]</li>\r\n	<li>Click Save to unzip the apache-ant-1.6.5-bin.zip [PGP] [SHA1] [MD5] file and save it to your C:/ directory as ant .</li>\r\n	<li>Add the <samp>bin</samp> directory to your <var>PATH</var> environment variable.</li>\r\n	<li>Add the <var>ANT_HOME</var> environment variable set to <samp>C:/ant</samp> .</li>\r\n	<li>Add the <var>ANT_OPTS</var> environment variable set to <samp>-Xmx256M</samp> .</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n2. com.sun.tools.javac.Main is not on the classpath. Perhaps JAVA_HOME does not point。\r\n\r\n解决方法是：\r\n\r\n</div>', '最新版 phoneGap Nodejs环境下 的安装流程总结', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '539-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-16 11:32:09', '2014-05-16 03:32:09', '', 539, 'http://www.joecora.com/?p=541', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(542, 1, '2014-05-16 11:37:27', '2014-05-16 03:37:27', '在win7下安装的步骤是：\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<pre><code>C:\\&gt; npm install -g phonegap</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<pre><code>$ phonegap create my-app\r\n$ cd my-app\r\n$ phonegap run android</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n但中间遇到许多问题，在这个环境下是遇到的问题及解决方式如下：\r\n\r\n<strong>1 . 大意是 ant 无法执行：</strong>\r\n\r\n解决方法是：下载最新版ant:  http://apache.fayea.com/apache-mirror//ant/binaries/apache-ant-1.9.4-bin.zip.\r\n<h1>Installing Ant on Windows</h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Enter the URL: <a href="http://ant.apache.org/bindownload.cgi" target="_blank">http://ant.apache.org/bindownload.cgi</a> .</li>\r\n	<li>On the Apache Ant Project page, find the heading Current Release of Ant .</li>\r\n	<li>Select apache-ant-1.6.5-bin.zip [PGP] [SHA1] [MD5]</li>\r\n	<li>Click Save to unzip the apache-ant-1.6.5-bin.zip [PGP] [SHA1] [MD5] file and save it to your C:/ directory as ant .</li>\r\n	<li>Add the <samp>bin</samp> directory to your <var>PATH</var> environment variable.</li>\r\n	<li>Add the <var>ANT_HOME</var> environment variable set to <samp>C:/ant</samp> .</li>\r\n	<li>Add the <var>ANT_OPTS</var> environment variable set to <samp>-Xmx256M</samp> .</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>2. com.sun.tools.javac.Main is not on the classpath. Perhaps JAVA_HOME does not point。</strong>\r\n\r\n解决方法是：把JAVA_HOME（java的安装目录）下的/lib/tools.jar复制到提示的JAVA_HOME所指向的路径。\r\n\r\n<strong>3.Error executing "adb devices": ''adb''</strong>\r\n\r\n解决方法是：将sdk\\platform-tools所对应的目录加入环境变量PATH(adt\\sdk\\tools也需要加入PATH)\r\n\r\n</div>', '最新版 phoneGap Nodejs环境下 的安装流程总结', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '539-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-16 11:37:27', '2014-05-16 03:37:27', '', 539, 'http://www.joecora.com/?p=542', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(543, 1, '2014-05-16 11:42:50', '2014-05-16 03:42:50', '在win7下安装的步骤是：\r\n\r\n一. 下载环境依赖的工具及包\r\n\r\n下载安装 <a href="http://www.eclipse.org/downloads/">Eclipse Classic</a>\r\n\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5;">下载安装 </span><a style="line-height: 1.5;" href="http://developer.android.com/sdk/index.html">Android SDK</a>\r\n\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5;">下载安装</span><a style="line-height: 1.5;" href="http://developer.android.com/sdk/eclipse-adt.html#installing">ADT Plugin</a>\r\n\r\n二. 此外还需要常规的Nodejs,NPM 等。利用NPM工具安装 最新的PhoneGap版本\r\n<div>\r\n<pre><code>C:\\&gt; npm install -g phonegap</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<pre><code>$ phonegap create my-app\r\n$ cd my-app\r\n$ phonegap run android</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n但中间遇到许多问题，在这个环境下是遇到的问题及解决方式如下：\r\n\r\n<strong>1 . 大意是 ant 无法执行：</strong>\r\n\r\n解决方法是：下载最新版ant:  http://apache.fayea.com/apache-mirror//ant/binaries/apache-ant-1.9.4-bin.zip.\r\n<h1>Installing Ant on Windows</h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Enter the URL: <a href="http://ant.apache.org/bindownload.cgi" target="_blank">http://ant.apache.org/bindownload.cgi</a> .</li>\r\n	<li>On the Apache Ant Project page, find the heading Current Release of Ant .</li>\r\n	<li>Select apache-ant-1.6.5-bin.zip [PGP] [SHA1] [MD5]</li>\r\n	<li>Click Save to unzip the apache-ant-1.6.5-bin.zip [PGP] [SHA1] [MD5] file and save it to your C:/ directory as ant .</li>\r\n	<li>Add the <samp>bin</samp> directory to your <var>PATH</var> environment variable.</li>\r\n	<li>Add the <var>ANT_HOME</var> environment variable set to <samp>C:/ant</samp> .</li>\r\n	<li>Add the <var>ANT_OPTS</var> environment variable set to <samp>-Xmx256M</samp> .</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>2. com.sun.tools.javac.Main is not on the classpath. Perhaps JAVA_HOME does not point。</strong>\r\n\r\n解决方法是：把JAVA_HOME（java的安装目录）下的/lib/tools.jar复制到提示的JAVA_HOME所指向的路径。\r\n\r\n<strong>3.Error executing "adb devices": ''adb''</strong>\r\n\r\n解决方法是：将sdk\\platform-tools所对应的目录加入环境变量PATH(adt\\sdk\\tools也需要加入PATH)\r\n\r\n</div>', '最新版 phoneGap android  Nodejs环境下 的安装流程总结', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '539-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-16 11:42:50', '2014-05-16 03:42:50', '', 539, 'http://www.joecora.com/?p=543', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(544, 1, '2014-05-16 11:44:18', '2014-05-16 03:44:18', '在win7下安装的步骤是：\r\n<h2>一. 下载环境依赖的工具及包</h2>\r\n下载安装 <a href="http://www.eclipse.org/downloads/">Eclipse Classic</a>\r\n\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5;">下载安装 </span><a style="line-height: 1.5;" href="http://developer.android.com/sdk/index.html">Android SDK</a>\r\n\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5;">下载安装</span><a style="line-height: 1.5;" href="http://developer.android.com/sdk/eclipse-adt.html#installing">ADT Plugin</a>\r\n<h2>二. 此外还需要常规的Nodejs,NPM 等。利用NPM工具安装 最新的PhoneGap版本</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n<pre><code>C:\\&gt; npm install -g phonegap</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<pre><code>$ phonegap create my-app\r\n$ cd my-app\r\n$ phonegap run android</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>三.但中间遇到许多问题，在这个环境下是遇到的问题及解决方式如下：</h2>\r\n<strong>1 . 大意是 ant 无法执行：</strong>\r\n\r\n解决方法是：下载最新版ant:  http://apache.fayea.com/apache-mirror//ant/binaries/apache-ant-1.9.4-bin.zip.\r\n<h4>Installing Ant on Windows</h4>\r\n<div>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Enter the URL: <a href="http://ant.apache.org/bindownload.cgi" target="_blank">http://ant.apache.org/bindownload.cgi</a> .</li>\r\n	<li>On the Apache Ant Project page, find the heading Current Release of Ant .</li>\r\n	<li>Select apache-ant-1.6.5-bin.zip [PGP] [SHA1] [MD5]</li>\r\n	<li>Click Save to unzip the apache-ant-1.6.5-bin.zip [PGP] [SHA1] [MD5] file and save it to your C:/ directory as ant .</li>\r\n	<li>Add the <samp>bin</samp> directory to your <var>PATH</var> environment variable.</li>\r\n	<li>Add the <var>ANT_HOME</var> environment variable set to <samp>C:/ant</samp> .</li>\r\n	<li>Add the <var>ANT_OPTS</var> environment variable set to <samp>-Xmx256M</samp> .</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>2. com.sun.tools.javac.Main is not on the classpath. Perhaps JAVA_HOME does not point。</strong>\r\n\r\n解决方法是：把JAVA_HOME（java的安装目录）下的/lib/tools.jar复制到提示的JAVA_HOME所指向的路径。\r\n\r\n<strong>3.Error executing "adb devices": ''adb''</strong>\r\n\r\n解决方法是：将sdk\\platform-tools所对应的目录加入环境变量PATH(adt\\sdk\\tools也需要加入PATH)\r\n\r\n</div>', '最新版 phoneGap android  Nodejs环境下 的安装流程总结', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '539-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-16 11:44:18', '2014-05-16 03:44:18', '', 539, 'http://www.joecora.com/?p=544', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(545, 1, '2014-05-16 11:45:01', '2014-05-16 03:45:01', '在win7下安装的步骤是：\r\n<h2>一. 下载环境依赖的工具及包</h2>\r\n下载安装 <a href="http://www.eclipse.org/downloads/">Eclipse Classic</a>\r\n\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5;">下载安装 </span><a style="line-height: 1.5;" href="http://developer.android.com/sdk/index.html">Android SDK</a>\r\n\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5;">下载安装</span><a style="line-height: 1.5;" href="http://developer.android.com/sdk/eclipse-adt.html#installing">ADT Plugin</a>\r\n<h2>二. 此外还需要常规的Nodejs,NPM 等。利用NPM工具安装 最新的PhoneGap版本</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n<code>C:\\&gt; npm install -g phonegap</code>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<code>$ phonegap create my-app\r\n$ cd my-app\r\n$ phonegap run android</code>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>三.但中间遇到许多问题，在这个环境下是遇到的问题及解决方式如下：</h2>\r\n<strong>1 . 大意是 ant 无法执行：</strong>\r\n\r\n解决方法是：下载最新版ant:  http://apache.fayea.com/apache-mirror//ant/binaries/apache-ant-1.9.4-bin.zip.\r\n<h4>Installing Ant on Windows</h4>\r\n<div>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Enter the URL: <a href="http://ant.apache.org/bindownload.cgi" target="_blank">http://ant.apache.org/bindownload.cgi</a> .</li>\r\n	<li>On the Apache Ant Project page, find the heading Current Release of Ant .</li>\r\n	<li>Select apache-ant-1.6.5-bin.zip [PGP] [SHA1] [MD5]</li>\r\n	<li>Click Save to unzip the apache-ant-1.6.5-bin.zip [PGP] [SHA1] [MD5] file and save it to your C:/ directory as ant .</li>\r\n	<li>Add the <samp>bin</samp> directory to your <var>PATH</var> environment variable.</li>\r\n	<li>Add the <var>ANT_HOME</var> environment variable set to <samp>C:/ant</samp> .</li>\r\n	<li>Add the <var>ANT_OPTS</var> environment variable set to <samp>-Xmx256M</samp> .</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>2. com.sun.tools.javac.Main is not on the classpath. Perhaps JAVA_HOME does not point。</strong>\r\n\r\n解决方法是：把JAVA_HOME（java的安装目录）下的/lib/tools.jar复制到提示的JAVA_HOME所指向的路径。\r\n\r\n<strong>3.Error executing "adb devices": ''adb''</strong>\r\n\r\n解决方法是：将sdk\\platform-tools所对应的目录加入环境变量PATH(adt\\sdk\\tools也需要加入PATH)\r\n\r\n</div>', '最新版 phoneGap android  Nodejs环境下 的安装流程总结', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '539-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-16 11:45:01', '2014-05-16 03:45:01', '', 539, 'http://www.joecora.com/?p=545', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `jc_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES
(549, 1, '2014-05-21 10:19:15', '2014-05-21 02:19:15', '基本结构：\r\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1">\r\n<!doctype html>\r\n<html lang="en">\r\n<head>\r\n        <!--html4 指定字符编码方式\r\n        <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=UTF-8">-->\r\n	<!--html5 指定字符编码方式-->\r\n        <meta charset="UTF-8">\r\n	<title>Document</title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n	\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n</code>\r\n\r\n<h2>可以省略的标记的元素</h2>\r\n1. 不允许写结束标记的元素： 比如<img />\r\n2. 可以省略结束标记的元素:  比如<li>\r\n3. 可以省略全部标记的元素:  比如html,head,body,tbody,colgroup\r\n\r\n<h2>可以省略属性值的属性</h2>\r\n所有具有boolean属性的属性可以省略值的书写\r\n以下checked 均为 true\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked>\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked="">\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked="checked">\r\n以下checked 均为 false\r\n<input type="checkbox">\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked="false">\r\n\r\n<h2>省略引号</h2>\r\n当属性值不包含运算符时可以省略引号\r\n<input type="checkbox">\r\n<input type=checkbox>', 'html5 标签语法上的变化', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '546-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-21 10:19:15', '2014-05-21 02:19:15', '', 546, 'http://www.joecora.com/?p=549', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(550, 1, '2014-05-21 10:22:21', '2014-05-21 02:22:21', '基本结构：\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1">\n<!doctype html>\n<html lang="en">\n<head>\n        <!--html4 指定字符编码方式\n        <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=UTF-8">-->\n	<!--html5 指定字符编码方式-->\n        <meta charset="UTF-8">\n	<title>Document</title>\n</head>\n<body>\n	\n</body>\n</html>\n</code>\n\n<h2>可以省略的标记的元素</h2>\n1. 不允许写结束标记的元素： 比如<img />\n2. 可以省略结束标记的元素:  比如<li>\n3. 可以省略全部标记的元素:  比如html,head,body,tbody,colgroup\n\n<h2>可以省略属性值的属性</h2>\n所有具有boolean属性的属性可以省略值的书写\n以下checked 均为 true\n<input type="checkbox" checked>\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox" checked></code>\n<input type="checkbox" checked="">\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox" checked=""></code>\n<input type="checkbox" checked="checked">\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"></code>\n以下checked 均为 false\n<input type="checkbox">\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox"></code>\n<input type="checkbox" checked="false">\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"> checked="false"</code>\n\n<h2>省略引号</h2>\n当属性值不包含运算符时可以省略引号\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"> checked="false"</code><input type="checkbox">\n<input type=checkbox>', 'html5 标签语法上的变化', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '546-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-05-21 10:22:21', '2014-05-21 02:22:21', '', 546, 'http://www.joecora.com/?p=550', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(556, 1, '2014-05-21 10:41:29', '2014-05-21 02:41:29', '基本结构：\r\n[ccenbwl_html]\r\n<!doctype html>\r\n<html lang="en">\r\n<head>\r\n        <!--html4 指定字符编码方式\r\n        <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=UTF-8">-->\r\n	<!--html5 指定字符编码方式-->\r\n        <meta charset="UTF-8">\r\n	<title>Document</title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n	\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n[/ccenbwl_html]\r\n\r\n<h2>可以省略的标记的元素</h2>\r\n1. 不允许写结束标记的元素： 比如[ccienbwl_html]<img />[/ccienbwl_html]\r\n2. 可以省略结束标记的元素:  比如[ccienbwl_html]<li>[/ccienbwl_html]\r\n3. 可以省略全部标记的元素:  比如html,head,body,tbody,colgroup\r\n\r\n<h2>可以省略属性值的属性</h2>\r\n所有具有boolean属性的属性可以省略值的书写\r\n<strong>以下checked 均为 true</strong>\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked> [ccienbwl_html]<input type="checkbox" checked>[/ccienbwl_html]\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked=""> [ccienbwl_html]<input type="checkbox" checked="">[/ccienbwl_html]\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked="checked"> [ccienbwl_html]<input type="checkbox" checked="checked">[/ccienbwl_html]\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked="false"> 注意这种情况 : [ccienbwl_html]<input type="checkbox" checked="false">[/ccienbwl_html]\r\n<strong>以下checked 均为 false</strong>\r\n<input type="checkbox"> [ccienbwl_html]<input type="checkbox">[/ccienbwl_html]\r\n\r\n<h2>省略引号</h2>\r\n当属性值不包含运算符时可以省略引号\r\n[ccienbwl_html]<input type="checkbox">[/ccienbwl_html] [ccienbwl_html]<input type=checkbox>[/ccienbwl_html]', 'html5 标签语法上的变化', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '546-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-21 10:41:29', '2014-05-21 02:41:29', '', 546, 'http://www.joecora.com/?p=556', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(551, 1, '2014-05-21 10:22:52', '2014-05-21 02:22:52', '基本结构：\r\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1">\r\n<!doctype html>\r\n<html lang="en">\r\n<head>\r\n        <!--html4 指定字符编码方式\r\n        <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=UTF-8">-->\r\n	<!--html5 指定字符编码方式-->\r\n        <meta charset="UTF-8">\r\n	<title>Document</title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n	\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n</code>\r\n\r\n<h2>可以省略的标记的元素</h2>\r\n1. 不允许写结束标记的元素： 比如<img />\r\n2. 可以省略结束标记的元素:  比如<li>\r\n3. 可以省略全部标记的元素:  比如html,head,body,tbody,colgroup\r\n\r\n<h2>可以省略属性值的属性</h2>\r\n所有具有boolean属性的属性可以省略值的书写\r\n以下checked 均为 true\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked>\r\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox" checked></code>\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked="">\r\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox" checked=""></code>\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked="checked">\r\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"></code>\r\n以下checked 均为 false\r\n<input type="checkbox">\r\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox"></code>\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked="false">\r\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox" checked="false"></code>\r\n\r\n<h2>省略引号</h2>\r\n当属性值不包含运算符时可以省略引号\r\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox"></code>\r\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type=checkbox></code>', 'html5 标签语法上的变化', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '546-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-21 10:22:52', '2014-05-21 02:22:52', '', 546, 'http://www.joecora.com/?p=551', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(552, 1, '2014-05-21 10:26:25', '2014-05-21 02:26:25', '基本结构：\r\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1">\r\n<!doctype html>\r\n<html lang="en">\r\n<head>\r\n        <!--html4 指定字符编码方式\r\n        <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=UTF-8">-->\r\n	<!--html5 指定字符编码方式-->\r\n        <meta charset="UTF-8">\r\n	<title>Document</title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n	\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n</code>\r\n\r\n<h2>可以省略的标记的元素</h2>\r\n1. 不允许写结束标记的元素： 比如<img />\r\n2. 可以省略结束标记的元素:  比如<li>\r\n3. 可以省略全部标记的元素:  比如html,head,body,tbody,colgroup\r\n\r\n<h2>可以省略属性值的属性</h2>\r\n所有具有boolean属性的属性可以省略值的书写\r\n以下checked 均为 true\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked> <code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox" checked></code>\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked=""> <code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox" checked=""></code>\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked="checked"> <code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"></code>\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked="false"> 注意这种情况 : <code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox" checked="false"></code>\r\n以下checked 均为 false\r\n<input type="checkbox">\r\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox"></code>\r\n\r\n<h2>省略引号</h2>\r\n当属性值不包含运算符时可以省略引号\r\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox"></code>\r\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type=checkbox></code>', 'html5 标签语法上的变化', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '546-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-21 10:26:25', '2014-05-21 02:26:25', '', 546, 'http://www.joecora.com/?p=552', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(554, 1, '2014-05-21 10:40:22', '2014-05-21 02:40:22', 'i – inline\r\ne – escaped\r\ns – strict\r\nn – line_numbers\r\nb – no_border\r\nw – no_wrap\r\nl – no_links\r\n基本结构：\r\n[ccenbwl_html]\r\n<!doctype html>\r\n<html lang="en">\r\n<head>\r\n        <!--html4 指定字符编码方式\r\n        <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=UTF-8">-->\r\n	<!--html5 指定字符编码方式-->\r\n        <meta charset="UTF-8">\r\n	<title>Document</title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n	\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n[/ccenbwl_html]\r\n\r\n<h2>可以省略的标记的元素</h2>\r\n1. 不允许写结束标记的元素： 比如[ccenbwl_html]<img />[/ccenbwl_html]\r\n2. 可以省略结束标记的元素:  比如[ccenbwl_html]<li>[/ccenbwl_html]\r\n3. 可以省略全部标记的元素:  比如html,head,body,tbody,colgroup\r\n\r\n<h2>可以省略属性值的属性</h2>\r\n所有具有boolean属性的属性可以省略值的书写\r\n<strong>以下checked 均为 true</strong>\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked> [ccienbwl_html]<input type="checkbox" checked>[/ccienbwl_html]\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked=""> [ccienbwl_html]<input type="checkbox" checked="">[/ccienbwl_html]\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked="checked"> [ccienbwl_html]<input type="checkbox" checked="checked">[/ccienbwl_html]\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked="false"> 注意这种情况 : [ccienbwl_html]<input type="checkbox" checked="false">[/ccienbwl_html]\r\n<strong>以下checked 均为 false</strong>\r\n<input type="checkbox"> [ccienbwl_html]<input type="checkbox">[/ccienbwl_html]\r\n\r\n<h2>省略引号</h2>\r\n当属性值不包含运算符时可以省略引号\r\n[ccienbwl_html]<input type="checkbox">[/ccienbwl_html] [ccienbwl_html]<input type=checkbox>[/ccienbwl_html]', 'html5 标签语法上的变化', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '546-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-21 10:40:22', '2014-05-21 02:40:22', '', 546, 'http://www.joecora.com/?p=554', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(553, 1, '2014-05-21 10:27:46', '2014-05-21 02:27:46', '基本结构：\r\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1">\r\n<!doctype html>\r\n<html lang="en">\r\n<head>\r\n        <!--html4 指定字符编码方式\r\n        <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=UTF-8">-->\r\n	<!--html5 指定字符编码方式-->\r\n        <meta charset="UTF-8">\r\n	<title>Document</title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n	\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n</code>\r\n\r\n<h2>可以省略的标记的元素</h2>\r\n1. 不允许写结束标记的元素： 比如<img />\r\n2. 可以省略结束标记的元素:  比如<li>\r\n3. 可以省略全部标记的元素:  比如html,head,body,tbody,colgroup\r\n\r\n<h2>可以省略属性值的属性</h2>\r\n所有具有boolean属性的属性可以省略值的书写\r\n<strong>以下checked 均为 true</strong>\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked> <code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox" checked></code>\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked=""> <code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox" checked=""></code>\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked="checked"> <code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"></code>\r\n<input type="checkbox" checked="false"> 注意这种情况 : <code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox" checked="false"></code>\r\n<strong>以下checked 均为 false</strong>\r\n<input type="checkbox">\r\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox"></code>\r\n\r\n<h2>省略引号</h2>\r\n当属性值不包含运算符时可以省略引号\r\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type="checkbox"></code>\r\n<code lang="javascript" height="auto" line_numbers="off" nowrap="0" noborder="1"><input type=checkbox></code>', 'html5 标签语法上的变化', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '546-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-21 10:27:46', '2014-05-21 02:27:46', '', 546, 'http://www.joecora.com/?p=553', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
